subject: Automobile Racing
organizations: National Assn of Stock Car Auto Racing
lead_paragraph: The latest feud in Nascar’s Sprint Cup Series involves Kyle Busch, 23, and Carl Edwards, 29, who had another run-in on Aug. 23 at Bristol.
